approach :- sliding window approach

1. ek set-collection-framework bnayenge aur 3 varible left = 0, right = 0, max = 0 lenge

2. right ko string ke end tk each element ke liye iterate krenge

3. yadi pariticular character of string ko set m add krne pr true aata h (means set m already esa koi character nhi h) 
    toh max (us particular substring m kitne char h) ki value calculate krenge
    formula :- Math.max(max, right-left+1)
    & right++ krenge

4. yadi false return hota h toh left pointer ki value ko increase krke set se element ko tb tk remove krenge jb tk ki vo particular duplicate character remove na ho jaye

